  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    [*] --> New : Process created\n    New --> Ready : Admit (admission scheduler)\n    Ready --> Running : Dispatch (scheduler)\n    Running --> Waiting : I/O or event wait\n    Running --> Ready : Interrupt (preemption)\n    Running --> Terminated : Exit (process completion)\n    \n    Waiting --> Ready : I/O completed\n    Waiting --> Suspended_Wait : Swap out (long-term scheduler)\n    Suspended_Wait --> Suspended_Ready : I/O completed\n    Suspended_Ready --> Ready : Swap in (long-term scheduler)\n    \n    Terminated --> [*]\n",
  "diagram_type": "size:500..600",
  "collected_at": "2026-02-27T03:24:01.395352",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个进程状态转换图，核心是要体现调度器的分层设计。 admission scheduler 负责从新建状态把进程接进系统，scheduler 做短程调度，还有 long-term scheduler 处理内存紧张时的换入换出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "admission scheduler",
        "scheduler",
        "long-term scheduler",
        "New",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是进程创建后的 New 状态，然后 admission scheduler 通过 Admit 动作把它送到 Ready 队列？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "New",
        "Ready",
        "Admit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Admit 是准入的意思。Ready 之后就是经典的 dispatch 到 Running，这个由 scheduler 完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Running",
        "Dispatch",
        "scheduler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把 Running 画出来，并且标上从 Ready 过来的 Dispatch 箭头。Running 之后有哪些出口？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Ready",
        "Dispatch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Running 有四个去向：正常结束走 Exit 到 Terminated；发起 I/O 就进入 Waiting；被抢占的话通过 Interrupt 回到 Ready；另外内存不足时还可能被换出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Terminated",
        "Waiting",
        "Ready",
        "Exit",
        "Interrupt",
        "I/O or event wait"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "抢占用 Interrupt 标注我理解了，但换出是不是应该归 long-term scheduler 管？它和直接回 Ready 的抢占要区分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Ready",
        "Interrupt",
        "preemption",
        "long-term scheduler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，long-term scheduler 只负责 swap 操作。Running 被抢占是 Interrupt，不涉及换出内存。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Interrupt",
        "preemption",
        "long-term scheduler",
        "swap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加 Running 到 Waiting 的 I/O or event wait，以及 Running 到 Terminated 的 Exit，标注了 process completion。现在处理 Waiting 状态的分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Waiting",
        "Terminated",
        "I/O or event wait",
        "Exit",
        "process completion"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Waiting 里的进程等 I/O 完成后回到 Ready。但如果系统内存压力大，long-term scheduler 可以把它 swap out 到 Suspended_Wait，这是挂起等待状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Waiting",
        "Ready",
        "I/O completed",
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Swap out",
        "long-term scheduler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Suspended_Wait 和普通的 Waiting 区别是后者还在内存里，前者被换到外存了？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Waiting",
        "swap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。Suspended_Wait 如果等的 I/O 完成了，它不会直接回 Ready，而是先变成 Suspended_Ready，等 swap in 才回到 Ready。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Suspended_Ready",
        "I/O completed",
        "Ready",
        "Swap in"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了：Waiting 到 Suspended_Wait 标注 Swap out，Suspended_Wait 到 Suspended_Ready 是 I/O completed，Suspended_Ready 到 Ready 是 Swap in，都注明 long-term scheduler。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Waiting",
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Suspended_Ready",
        "Ready",
        "Swap out",
        "Swap in",
        "long-term scheduler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还差起点和终点。进程创建从起始节点进入 New，Terminated 之后要回到终止节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "New",
        "Process created",
        "Terminated",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Terminated 到终止节点不需要标注动作吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Terminated",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不需要，空箭头就行。另外检查一下：Running 到 Ready 的 Interrupt 旁边要注明 preemption，强调是抢占。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Ready",
        "Interrupt",
        "preemption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "发现个问题，我刚才把 Running 到 Ready 只写了 Interrupt，没加 preemption 说明。现在补上。还有别的要调整吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Ready",
        "Interrupt",
        "preemption"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没了，这样层级很清晰：admission scheduler 管准入，scheduler 管 CPU 调度，long-term scheduler 管内存换入换出，三种挂起状态也都覆盖了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "admission scheduler",
        "scheduler",
        "long-term scheduler",
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Suspended_Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部完成，我最后核对一遍：New→Ready(Admit)，Ready→Running(Dispatch)，Running 四路分支，Waiting 和 Suspended 的转换，Terminated 收尾。",
      "elements_involved": [
